# Project Context — Research + Conventions

Before working on any project, research and save context.

- Before starting work: research project structure, patterns, configs
- Save findings to PROJECT_CONVENTIONS.md in the project root
- Keep conventions up to date as the project evolves
- Always re-read conventions before starting new work sessions
- Check existing patterns before creating new files
- When conventions are missing or stale, create/update them
